D. 2. 24. 59, and by Ho- race's own ‘Fomenta volnus nil malum levantia⁷ Epod. 11. 25, where the last words answer to the general epithet ‘ frigida.’ The sense will then be ¹ Yon are sure to win distinction, if that is your aim, in oratory, jmisprudence, poetry.
